{"tid":1653032,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"受惠於中美貿易戰，韓國三星超過中國華為成為全球5G王者","createTime":"2019-10-14T02:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T12:54:24.000Z","uid":155095,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"07cb4838e78599e6d9e0863926307e8590549d95","tid":1653032,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:10:27.000Z","msg":"近年全球設備商爭相開發5G技術，覬覦5G電訊市場的龍頭寶座。全球市場研究公司Dell'Oro公布，5G電訊設備由去年第4季至今年第1季的市場份額，<span style=\"color: red;\">當中三星電子稱霸「一哥」，市佔達37%，華為以28%屈居第二，其次是愛立信（27%）以及諾基亞（8%）</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_16x9_1024_578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aefimagesnew/aef_image/huawei-vs-samsung.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_16x9_1024_578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faefimagesnew%2Faef_image%2Fhuawei-vs-samsung.png&h=726521ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三星電子今年4月首次亮相商用5G服務，在網絡設備、晶片組和智能電話等產品線，皆採用5G技術。目前該公司已經跟美國Verizon、AT&amp;T及Sprint簽訂5G設備合同，最近亦宣布向日本電訊運營商KDDI提供價值20億美元的5G電訊設備。目標明年年底在全球電訊設備市場佔據20%份額。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cnba.live/images/image/36/3608428.jpg?t=1523078799\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnba.live%2Fimages%2Fimage%2F36%2F3608428.jpg%3Ft%3D1523078799&h=0516559f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實撇除5G技術，三星電子一直在整體電訊設備市場都處於弱勢位置。根據市場研究機構IHS Markit數據顯示，<span style=\"color: green;\">去年全球電訊設備份額，華為以31%名列第一，三星僅佔6.6%市場份額</span>。不過，隨著三星電子大量投資5G技術，同時受惠美國以安全為由制裁華為，要求盟國抵制華為5G設備，造就三星電子成為目前5G市場的王者。"},{"pid":"ded9e867e9d178717cde56af55b2401565fdbb8c","tid":1653032,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:23:23.000Z","msg":"歐美企喺5G爭奪戰真係收哂皮"},{"pid":"037cd923bb5a7661bc49459eb37dcb138e08e1b6","tid":1653032,"uid":12628,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"ded9e867e9d178717cde56af55b2401565fdbb8c","tid":1653032,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:23:23.000Z","msg":"歐美企喺5G爭奪戰真係收哂皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:44:28.000Z","msg":"人地正常做生意，有成本有風險，你屎為中共國家補貼，不正常低價搶標，霸地標，不公正競爭，外國私企點鬥"},{"pid":"b25b4df002f5d5f142095143d394a878d2ba79b9","tid":1653032,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ded9e867e9d178717cde56af55b2401565fdbb8c","tid":1653032,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:23:23.000Z","msg":"歐美企喺5G爭奪戰真係收哂皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:50:27.000Z","msg":"得<strong>愛立信</strong>（27%）同<strong>諾基亞</strong>（8%）<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d0e94f171e9a25449d516f40c6bf6e9432ab34","tid":1653032,"uid":275238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"三叔諗唔到咁樣番身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49fd8005b87a285d2d449e2c3d7759b7a3e3d467","tid":1653032,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5d0e94f171e9a25449d516f40c6bf6e9432ab34","tid":1653032,"uid":275238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"三叔諗唔到咁樣番身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T09:17:06.000Z","msg":"仲有Google封殺華為<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2816034/org/1d6798a28a9a0a9564321f01e09ecdc3.jpeg/pTt-7ZUBWPYq4VrBvpgkbvnBnCby-ewiaC0-8mgtPvI?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2816034%2Forg%2F1d6798a28a9a0a9564321f01e09ecdc3.jpeg%2FpTt-7ZUBWPYq4VrBvpgkbvnBnCby-ewiaC0-8mgtPvI%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=a7b5ce38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.cnbetacdn.com/article/2019/0504/c4e55e4b70b8a69.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.cnbetacdn.com%2Farticle%2F2019%2F0504%2Fc4e55e4b70b8a69.png&h=d3cdd121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d963321eacb645ffd281